object.customQuery:
Select distinct
t.SystemId,
t.ParentId,
t.Id,
t.Name,
t.AddDt,
t.AddTm,
t.CompleteDt,
t.CompleteTm,
t.CurrentOwner,
t.AddedByUserId,
t.Status,
t.Description,
t.WorkDt,
t.OriginalOwner,
t.Text,
t.Note,
t.Priority,
case when AddDt is null or CompleteDt is null then NULL else count(lkp_calendar.date) end as DaysToComplete,
t.AgencyCd,
t.AgencyGroupCd
from
dbo.task_stg t
left join
(select distinct date from dbo.lkp_calendar
where Holiday_Ind = 'N'
and Weekend_Ind = 'N')
lkp_calendar
on lkp_calendar.date >= t.AddDt
and lkp_calendar.date < t.CompleteDt
where t.id in
(select distinct ParentId from dbo.tasklink_stg) 
group by 
t.SystemId,
t.ParentId,
t.Id,
t.Name,
t.AddDt,
t.AddTm,
t.CompleteDt,
t.CompleteTm,
t.CurrentOwner,
t.AddedByUserId,
t.Status,
t.Description,
t.WorkDt,
t.OriginalOwner,
t.Text,
t.Note,
t.Priority,
t.AgencyCd,
t.AgencyGroupCd
